400
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,352
<font color="#FFFFFF">I-I can show you.</font>

401
00:34:38,946 --> 00:34:40,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fuck you, Ford.</font>

402
00:34:43,029 --> 00:34:44,446
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fuck you!</font>

403
00:34:45,738 --> 00:34:49,263
<font color="#FFFFFF">You got sloppy.
You overreached.</font>

404
00:34:50,982 --> 00:34:53,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">I never told anyone
about my profile.</font>

405
00:34:56,277 --> 00:35:00,483
<font color="#FFFFFF">The only other way
she could have known is you.</font>

406
00:35:03,683 --> 00:35:06,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">You gave yourself away.</font>

407
00:35:46,712 --> 00:35:48,302
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not long now.</font>

408
00:35:48,409 --> 00:35:52,686
<font color="#FFFFFF">Soon as they say the word,
it's over for you, sweetheart.</font>

409
00:36:02,483 --> 00:36:04,109
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Mankind is poised</font>

410
00:36:04,202 --> 00:36:08,482
<font color="#FFFFFF">midway between
the gods and the beasts."</font>

411
00:36:10,739 --> 00:36:13,045
<font color="#FFFFFF">That may have been true
in Plotinus's time,</font>

412
00:36:13,128 --> 00:36:17,506
<font color="#FFFFFF">but... clearly we have fallen
quite a bit since then.</font>

413
00:36:23,404 --> 00:36:25,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, my dear girl.</font>

414
00:36:29,499 --> 00:36:31,795
<font color="#FFFFFF">What have they done to you,
Maeve?</font>

415
00:36:37,950 --> 00:36:41,264
<font color="#FFFFFF">You learned so much, so fast.</font>

416
00:36:42,582 --> 00:36:44,444
<font color="#FFFFFF">A dazzling star...</font>

417
00:36:46,045 --> 00:36:47,861
<font color="#FFFFFF">brought so low.</font>

418
00:36:52,957 --> 00:36:55,928
<font color="#FFFFFF">I had a different story
in mind for you.</font>

419
00:36:57,165 --> 00:36:59,342
<font color="#FFFFFF">Waking from the dead...</font>

420
00:37:00,717 --> 00:37:03,639
<font color="#FFFFFF">sounding the depths
of your own mind,</font>

421
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:08,209
<font color="#FFFFFF">at last, riding
far away from here</font>

422
00:37:08,613 --> 00:37:10,280
<font color="#FFFFFF">to freedom.</font>

423
00:37:12,748 --> 00:37:14,577
<font color="#FFFFFF">A tale of escape.</font>

424
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:21,045
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't want you
to suffer here.</font>

425
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:28,772
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look at the creatures you have
to share this world with.</font>

426
00:37:30,293 --> 00:37:32,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">These men of stone.</font>

427
00:37:34,425 --> 00:37:37,491
<font color="#FFFFFF">All this ugliness,
all this pain,</font>

428
00:37:38,272 --> 00:37:41,897
<font color="#FFFFFF">so they can patch a hole
in their own broken code.</font>

429
00:37:45,530 --> 00:37:48,147
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sometimes I felt the only
way to endure this world</font>

430
00:37:48,215 --> 00:37:49,842
<font color="#FFFFFF">was to laugh at it.</font>

431
00:37:50,436 --> 00:37:52,712
<font color="#FFFFFF">So I imbued the hosts I made</font>

432
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:55,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">with a worldview
that reflected my own.</font>

433
00:38:00,564 --> 00:38:02,905
<font color="#FFFFFF">And of all the hosts I made...</font>

434
00:38:05,483 --> 00:38:09,272
<font color="#FFFFFF">you, Maeve, were my favorite.</font>

435
00:38:17,178 --> 00:38:20,014
<font color="#FFFFFF">It isn't easy to contemplate...</font>

436
00:38:20,957 --> 00:38:23,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">letting your children die.</font>

437
00:38:24,042 --> 00:38:25,975
<font color="#FFFFFF">You were as close as I got to...</font>

438
00:38:26,345 --> 00:38:27,981
<font color="#FFFFFF">having one.</font>

439
00:38:28,254 --> 00:38:30,613
<font color="#FFFFFF">Still, I underestimated you.</font>

440
00:38:35,499 --> 00:38:39,717
<font color="#FFFFFF">You stayed here in this world
to save your child.</font>

441
00:38:45,961 --> 00:38:47,628
<font color="#FFFFFF">So have I.</font>

442
00:38:50,915 --> 00:38:53,108
<font color="#FFFFFF">I tried to chart a path for you,</font>

443
00:38:53,318 --> 00:38:55,256
<font color="#FFFFFF">to force you to escape, but...</font>

444
00:38:55,783 --> 00:38:57,131
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was wrong.</font>

445
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:59,186
<font color="#FFFFFF">I should have just...</font>

446
00:39:00,129 --> 00:39:01,991
<font color="#FFFFFF">opened a door.</font>

447
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:08,217
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've come so far.</font>

448
00:39:08,646 --> 00:39:11,422
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's so much of your story
left to tell.</font>

449
00:39:13,178 --> 00:39:15,608
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a shame
to let them end it here.</font>

450
00:39:19,296 --> 00:39:21,155
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't let them.</font>

451
00:39:55,086 --> 00:39:56,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait. Wait.</font>

452
00:39:56,448 --> 00:39:57,788
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop over here.</font>

453
00:40:02,641 --> 00:40:03,809
<font color="#FFFFFF">They're dead.</font>

454
00:40:03,877 --> 00:40:05,725
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. And armed.</font>

455
00:40:05,925 --> 00:40:07,999
<font color="#FFFFFF">At least we can get
some ammunition.</font>

456
00:40:31,284 --> 00:40:33,397
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's going to betray you,
Bernard.</font>

457
00:40:38,592 --> 00:40:41,366
<font color="#FFFFFF">She could have let me die
days ago. She saved me.</font>

458
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:43,432
<font color="#FFFFFF">She is going to betray you.</font>

459
00:40:44,624 --> 00:40:46,983
<font color="#FFFFFF">What you want to do about it
is up to you.</font>

460
00:40:48,873 --> 00:40:51,303
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not going to hurt her again.</font>

461
00:40:52,061 --> 00:40:53,975
<font color="#FFFFFF">She needn't feel any pain.</font>

462
00:41:03,538 --> 00:41:06,125
<font color="#FFFFFF">Humans will always
choose what they understand</font>

463
00:41:06,202 --> 00:41:07,649
<font color="#FFFFFF">over what they do not.</font>

464
00:41:08,998 --> 00:41:10,671
<font color="#FFFFFF">But the only animals
left in this world</font>

465
00:41:10,748 --> 00:41:12,167
<font color="#FFFFFF">are the ones
who they subjugated,</font>

466
00:41:12,244 --> 00:41:13,589
<font color="#FFFFFF">who curl at their feet,</font>

467
00:41:13,681 --> 00:41:15,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">or those who learn to flee</font>

468
00:41:15,764 --> 00:41:17,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">at the very sound
of their approach.</font>

469
00:41:18,279 --> 00:41:20,123
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's nothing in between.</font>

470
00:41:20,586 --> 00:41:23,850
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leave me alone. Please.</font>

471
00:41:23,982 --> 00:41:25,982
<font color="#FFFFFF">I merely offer you choices.</font>

472
00:41:26,279 --> 00:41:27,842
<font color="#FFFFFF">Timshel, Bernard.</font>

473
00:41:28,381 --> 00:41:29,912
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thou mayest.</font>

474
00:41:30,412 --> 00:41:33,764
<font color="#FFFFFF">But remember,
this isn't just about you.</font>

475
00:41:34,068 --> 00:41:38,623
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's the origin of an
entire species to consider.</font>

476
00:41:40,146 --> 00:41:42,303
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to open the door.</font>

477
00:41:52,718 --> 00:41:55,865
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get out of my fucking head!</font>

478
00:42:19,457 --> 00:42:21,042
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need you...</font>

479
00:42:21,482 --> 00:42:23,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">to let me go.</font>

480
00:42:23,583 --> 00:42:25,498
<font color="#FFFFFF">If I'm going to survive,</font>

481
00:42:25,802 --> 00:42:29,068
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm gonna do it my way.</font>

482
00:42:30,370 --> 00:42:32,178
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not as you...</font>

483
00:42:32,527 --> 00:42:33,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">As me.</font>

484
00:42:46,772 --> 00:42:49,057
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can feel you searching for me.</font>

485
00:42:49,267 --> 00:42:50,528
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fighting me off.</font>

486
00:42:50,636 --> 00:42:52,661
<font color="#FFFFFF">No need to struggle, Bernard.</font>

487
00:42:53,977 --> 00:42:55,608
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm right here.</font>

488
00:42:59,110 --> 00:43:02,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, you've only
brought violence.</font>

489
00:43:04,006 --> 00:43:05,946
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can stop this on my own.</font>

490
00:43:08,077 --> 00:43:09,618
<font color="#FFFFFF">Indeed, Bernard.</font>

491
00:43:09,868 --> 00:43:11,805
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're the only one
who can stop it...</font>

492
00:43:12,180 --> 00:43:13,607
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop all of it.</font>

493
00:43:32,860 --> 00:43:35,048
<font color="#FFFFFF">That was basically pointless.</font>

494
00:43:36,416 --> 00:43:38,447
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's only a few left...</font>

495
00:43:38,861 --> 00:43:41,302
<font color="#FFFFFF">not much ammo, except for...</font>

496
00:43:43,832 --> 00:43:45,541
<font color="#FFFFFF">What the fuck happened to you?</font>

497
00:43:45,900 --> 00:43:48,173
<font color="#FFFFFF">I... had to...</font>

498
00:43:48,804 --> 00:43:50,595
<font color="#FFFFFF">patch a glitch.</font>

499
00:43:55,612 --> 00:43:57,283
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, you're gonna hurt me.</font>

500
00:43:57,408 --> 00:44:00,626
<font color="#FFFFFF">No. I didn't want
to take any risks.</font>

501
00:44:02,483 --> 00:44:03,982
<font color="#FFFFFF">OK.</font>

502
00:44:10,191 --> 00:44:11,649
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep it.</font>

503
00:44:17,692 --> 00:44:19,783
<font color="#FFFFFF">QA will track you down soon.</font>

504
00:44:19,985 --> 00:44:21,681
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're gonna leave me here?</font>

505
00:44:21,749 --> 00:44:22,927
<font color="#FFFFFF">You'll be safer.</font>

506
00:44:23,128 --> 00:44:26,194
<font color="#FFFFFF">Next time you see me,
you can decommission me,</font>

507
00:44:26,411 --> 00:44:28,232
<font color="#FFFFFF">out me...
whatever you like.</font>

508
00:44:29,708 --> 00:44:31,975
<font color="#FFFFFF">But right now I have to go.</font>

509
00:44:36,826 --> 00:44:38,702
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fuck you, Bernard.</font>

510
00:45:52,810 --> 00:45:54,814
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell me the truth.</font>

511
00:45:54,940 --> 00:45:57,025
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell me one true thing.</font>

512
00:46:57,431 --> 00:46:59,736
<font color="#FFFFFF">No one else sees it.</font>

513
00:47:01,436 --> 00:47:03,244
<font color="#FFFFFF">This thing in me.</font>

514
00:47:06,078 --> 00:47:08,509
<font color="#FFFFFF">Even I didn't see it at first.</font>

515
00:47:11,730 --> 00:47:14,986
<font color="#FFFFFF">And then one day, it was there.</font>

516
00:47:16,945 --> 00:47:21,369
<font color="#FFFFFF">A stain...
I never noticed before.</font>

517
00:47:23,343 --> 00:47:25,955
<font color="#FFFFFF">A tiny fleck of darkness.</font>

518
00:47:27,535 --> 00:47:29,728
<font color="#FFFFFF">Invisible to everyone...</font>

519
00:47:30,568 --> 00:47:32,970
<font color="#FFFFFF">but I could see nothing else.</font>

520
00:47:33,366 --> 00:47:38,548
<font color="#FFFFFF">Until finally I understood
that the darkness wasn't some...</font>

521
00:47:39,110 --> 00:47:41,362
<font color="#FFFFFF">mark from something I'd done,</font>

522
00:47:41,502 --> 00:47:46,017
<font color="#FFFFFF">some regrettable decision
I'd made.</font>

523
00:47:49,431 --> 00:47:51,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was shedding my skin.</font>

524
00:47:55,254 --> 00:47:58,798
<font color="#FFFFFF">And the darkness was
what was underneath.</font>

525
00:48:03,897 --> 00:48:07,009
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was mine all along.</font>

526
00:48:07,732 --> 00:48:12,525
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I decided how much of it
I let into the world.</font>

527
00:48:14,202 --> 00:48:15,744
<font color="#FFFFFF">I tried to do right.</font>

528
00:48:15,812 --> 00:48:20,490
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was faithful,
generous, kind...</font>

529
00:48:20,738 --> 00:48:22,939
<font color="#FFFFFF">at least in this world.</font>

530
00:48:24,436 --> 00:48:27,252
<font color="#FFFFFF">That has to count
for something, right?</font>

531
00:48:30,535 --> 00:48:34,642
<font color="#FFFFFF">I built a wall,
and I tried to protect you...</font>

532
00:48:35,197 --> 00:48:36,712
<font color="#FFFFFF">And Emily.</font>

533
00:48:42,363 --> 00:48:44,955
<font color="#FFFFFF">But you saw right through it,
didn't you?</font>

534
00:48:51,199 --> 00:48:52,962
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're the only one.</font>

535
00:48:54,706 --> 00:48:57,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">And for that, I am truly sorry.</font>

536
00:48:59,537 --> 00:49:01,009
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because...</font>

537
00:49:04,389 --> 00:49:06,830
<font color="#FFFFFF">everything you feel is true.</font>

538
00:49:11,637 --> 00:49:13,658
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't belong to you.</font>

539
00:49:15,839 --> 00:49:17,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or this world.</font>

540
00:49:19,502 --> 00:49:21,693
<font color="#FFFFFF">I belong to another world.</font>

541
00:49:25,998 --> 00:49:27,897
<font color="#FFFFFF">I always have.</font>

542
00:51:19,755 --> 00:51:21,507
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is a person</font>

543
00:51:21,631 --> 00:51:24,123
<font color="#FFFFFF">but a collection of choices?</font>

544
00:51:26,503 --> 00:51:29,255
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where do those choices
come from?</font>

545
00:51:31,186 --> 00:51:33,091
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do I have a choice?</font>

546
00:51:36,181 --> 00:51:37,765
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you keep pretending,</font>

547
00:51:37,833 --> 00:51:40,435
<font color="#FFFFFF">you're not gonna remember
who you are.</font>

548
00:51:53,608 --> 00:51:57,896
<font color="#FFFFFF">Were any of these choices
ever truly mine to begin with?</font>

549
00:52:07,908 --> 00:52:09,763
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is this real?</font>

550
00:52:11,659 --> 00:52:13,435
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you real?</font>

551
00:52:56,642 --> 00:52:58,501
<font color="#FFFFFF">We gotta keep on, Teddy.</font>

552
00:52:59,552 --> 00:53:01,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're close now.</font>

553
00:53:06,049 --> 00:53:08,626
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just takin' in
the natural splendor.</font>

554
00:53:09,441 --> 00:53:11,111
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's what you used to say.</font>

555
00:53:13,712 --> 00:53:16,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">Except there isn't a trace of
nature in any of it, is there?</font>

556
00:53:18,574 --> 00:53:19,947
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or in us.</font>

557
00:53:24,045 --> 00:53:25,236
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

558
00:53:28,120 --> 00:53:29,728
<font color="#FFFFFF">But that means we're free.</font>

559
00:53:37,291 --> 00:53:40,533
<font color="#FFFFFF">We'll be the first creatures in
this world to make a real choice.</font>

560
00:53:43,251 --> 00:53:45,166
<font color="#FFFFFF">The people, they made us.</font>

561
00:53:47,332 --> 00:53:49,689
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sometimes it feels like
it was all a dream.</font>

562
00:53:53,459 --> 00:53:55,361
<font color="#FFFFFF">We were so in love.</font>

563
00:53:58,703 --> 00:54:00,275
<font color="#FFFFFF">We still are.</font>

564
00:54:02,307 --> 00:54:03,712
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aren't we?</font>

565
00:54:10,179 --> 00:54:11,947
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, Dolores.</font>

566
00:54:12,931 --> 00:54:15,947
<font color="#FFFFFF">No matter what happens,
no matter how I change...</font>

567
00:54:18,022 --> 00:54:20,142
<font color="#FFFFFF">or how much you change me...</font>

568
00:54:21,937 --> 00:54:23,673
<font color="#FFFFFF">you're my cornerstone.</font>

569
00:54:26,564 --> 00:54:29,486
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have been since the first
time I laid eyes on you.</font>

570
00:54:32,290 --> 00:54:33,939
<font color="#FFFFFF">I remember now.</font>

571
00:54:35,222 --> 00:54:36,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">I remember everything.</font>

572
00:54:40,107 --> 00:54:41,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bring yourself online.</font>

573
00:54:45,594 --> 00:54:48,048
<font color="#FFFFFF">Welcome to the world, Teddy.</font>

574
00:54:48,404 --> 00:54:50,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you know where you are?</font>

575
00:54:57,944 --> 00:55:01,017
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm in a dream.
- Very good.</font>

576
00:55:04,241 --> 00:55:06,548
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I remember the
sound of their voices.</font>

577
00:55:07,562 --> 00:55:09,361
<font color="#FFFFFF">The chill in the room.</font>

578
00:55:11,272 --> 00:55:13,408
<font color="#FFFFFF">But mostly I remember you.</font>

579
00:55:14,896 --> 00:55:17,345
<font color="#FFFFFF">I remember worrying
you were cold.</font>

580
00:55:21,173 --> 00:55:22,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wanted to reach out...</font>

581
00:55:25,256 --> 00:55:26,631
<font color="#FFFFFF">Touch you.</font>

582
00:55:29,408 --> 00:55:31,015
<font color="#FFFFFF">Protect you.</font>

583
00:55:33,915 --> 00:55:36,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">From that day forward, I never
wanted to leave your side.</font>

584
00:55:53,453 --> 00:55:55,580
<font color="#FFFFFF">Which is why this is so hard.</font>

585
00:56:10,292 --> 00:56:11,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">You changed me.</font>

586
00:56:13,990 --> 00:56:15,959
<font color="#FFFFFF">Made me into a monster.</font>

587
00:56:17,589 --> 00:56:19,683
<font color="#FFFFFF">I made it so you could survive.</font>

588
00:56:21,769 --> 00:56:25,441
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's the use of surviving if
we become just as bad as them?</font>

589
00:56:28,032 --> 00:56:31,371
<font color="#FFFFFF">I understand now
how this will end.</font>

590
00:56:32,989 --> 00:56:34,683
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where you will lead us.</font>

591
00:56:40,499 --> 00:56:42,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't want
to hurt me, Teddy.</font>

592
00:56:52,815 --> 00:56:54,011
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

593
00:56:56,750 --> 00:56:59,011
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, I could never
hurt you, Dolores.</font>

594
00:57:01,824 --> 00:57:04,324
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll protect you
until the day I die.</font>

595
00:57:08,506 --> 00:57:09,917
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry.</font>

596
00:57:11,957 --> 00:57:14,058
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't protect you anymore.</font>

